<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Invoice for Your Course Purchase</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: white;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 300;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 30px;
      }

      .content h2 {
        color: #667eea;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .course-details {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
      }

      .course-details h3 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .course-details p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        color: #666;
      }

      .invoice-link {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .invoice-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #666;
        border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      }

      .footer p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .transaction-id {
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        background-color: #e9ecef;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        <p>Thank you for your course purchase</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Dear <%= customerName %>,</h2>

        <p>
          We're excited to confirm that your payment has been successfully
          processed! You now have full access to your course.
        </p>

        <div class="course-details">
          <h3>Course Details:</h3>
          <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= courseName %></p>
          <p>
            <strong>Transaction ID:</strong>
            <span class="transaction-id"><%= transactionId %></span>
          </p>
          <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> $<%= amount %></p>
          <p>
            <strong>Purchase Date:</strong> <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString()
            %>
          </p>
        </div>

        <p>
          Your invoice has been generated and is attached to this email. You can
          also download it anytime from the link below:
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <a href="<%= invoiceUrl %>" class="invoice-link" target="_blank">
            Download Invoice
          </a>
        </div>

        <p>
          You can now access your course from your dashboard. Start learning and
          take your skills to the next level!
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to
          contact our support team.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px">
          Happy learning!<br />
          <strong>The SHIKHI Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SHIKHI. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
